            <description><![CDATA[
                            <h2>New Features</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Adds special Dock icons that can be unlocked</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2>Fixes and Improvements</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Adds names to all Dock icons in the settings</li>
                                <li>Disables the state toggles for untitled goals</li>
                                <li>Fixes an issue where a new goal would sometimes not be added at the end of the list</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2>Known Issues</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>When the list is not scrolled to the top, the burning animation may appear incorrectly</li>
                            </ul>
							]]></description>
